<div id="our-story" class="container">
    <div class="our-story-title">
        <h1 class="display-3">Our Story</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="our-story-content">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-3">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="aboutusImage\photo for about us.jpg" alt="about us photo">
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
                    <h3>"We guide university students to a greater dressing culture."</h3>
                    <div class="col-9 ">
                        <p>As a uni student, we saw many other students out there have no idea how to dress up
                            themselves.
                            Some
                            students simply just wear shorts and polo tee to attend classes, which is a no go to attract
                            people's attention. Our name comes from the words 'university' and 'clothing' - simple and
                            strong.
                            What we wear can define who we are. Our goal is to guide students start dressing
                            appropriately.
                            We
                            also make our clothing comfortable and light so that our students can withstand the hot
                            weather
                            from
                            Malaysia.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

