                <h4>August 2018</h4>
                <p>We met each other during orientation in Sunway University. We knew each other because we are from
                    the
                    same
                    course.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-6">
                <h4>November 2018</h4>
                <p>We realize that many students in Sunway University especially men are bad at dressing themselves.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-6">
                <h4>January 2019</h4>
                <p>We decided to create our own brand to encourage other people to dress nicely. We started
                    designing
                    our
                    clothes
                    and find sponsors for our first batch of clohting</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-6">
                <h4>March 2019</h4>
                <p>We release our clothing and we were getting really good feedback from our customers. Many of
                    Sunway
                    students
                    bought our clothing and we started seeing more and more people wearing it in campus.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
